nodes.text: Star Wars Miniatures: The Clone Wars Miniatures Map Pack

Star Wars Miniatures: The Clone Wars Map Pack is a map pack containing two collectible miniatures released in 2009. Each Map Pack contains two collectible miniatures, two stat cards, and one double-sided battle map.
